RentAmount(oliveGarden, 2000).
Fluffy(fluffy).
Tom(tom).
Cat(fluffy).
Pet(fluffy).
Owns(tom, fluffy).

∀x (ManagedBuilding(x) → DepositRequired(x)).

# The security deposit is either equal to or greater than one month's rent.
∀x (DepositRequired(x) → (DepositEqualToOneMonthRent(x) ∨ DepositGreaterThanOneMonthRent(x))).

∀x (ManagedBuilding(x) → (Rent(tom, x) ↔ (AllowedPet(fluffy, x) ∧ ∃d (DepositAmount(x, d) ∧ LessThan(d, 1500))))).

AllowedPet(fluffy, oliveGarden)
